We say our witch hazel is the highest grade available, but what does that mean?!

💛 We distill our witch hazel to meet the highest standards of purity, according to USP (U.S. Pharmacopeia), which sets the standards for active ingredients.
💛 Unlike some brands that list water as their top toner ingredient, ours is all-natural witch hazel. True love is never watered down.
💛 This means you’re getting real witch hazel that is the most potent and effective for your skin. We like to keep it 💯 around here. Xoxo
